         <abstract>
            <p>An adapted finite element method is proposed for a class of elliptic problems with singular data. The idea is to subtract the main singularity from the solution and to solve for the remainder using suitable mesh-refinements. Optimal order error estimates are proved.</p>
          </abstract>
